&nbsp;
The students involved in the survey are about 561.265 of 5,799 schools and will support the tests of Italian, Mathematics and English (reading and listening) to the computer. On today's day, 51,000 tests were carried out and everything was done regularly. As already happened for the survey of the students of the last year of secondary school of second degree, the constant collaboration between the educational institutions, the Ministry of Education and Merit and the Invalsi has allowed to reach this year's appointment in the most appropriate organizational conditions and the students to face the best and serenely this stage propedeutic to the end of the cycle.
